title: Brett Eldredge Stops By + Bobby Reunites With Sharna Burgess
itunes:title: Brett Eldredge Stops By + Bobby Reunites With Sharna Burgess
description:
Brett Eldredge stops by the studio to talk about his Glow Deluxe album. Also, Bobby reunites with his Dancing With The Stars partner Sharna Burgess for the first time since the show ended.
